otu.label: Noturus hildebrandi
otu.meta: "We examined both subspecies of N. hildebrandi, N. h. hildebrandi (Bailey & Taylor, 1950) and N. h. latus Taylor, 1969, but treated them as a single taxon in the analyses." (Egge and Simmons 2009, page 62) Noturus hildebrandi hildebrandi: JFBM 41871 (6 c.s.), USNM 172031 (3 c.s.), JFBM 37563 (9 alc.), JFBM 42758 (1 alc.), JFBM 42783 (7 alc.). Noturus hildebrandi latus: JFBM 40909 (1 c.s.), JFBM 42682 (14 alc.), JFBM 42700 (4 alc.), JFBM 40860 (1 alc.), JFBM 42727 (2 alc.). Noturus hildebrandi x latus: USNM 193470 (1 c.s.), JFBM 37538 (1 alc.), JFBM 40769 (4 alc.).
